title: Where's My Man To-Nite (1943) SPENCER WILLIAMS

sources.title: Where's My Man To-Nite (1943) SPENCER WILLIAMS
sources.description:
BLACK HISTORY MONTH
Writer/Director: Spencer Williams
Stars: Emmet Jackson, George T. Sutton, L.K. Smith


During World War II, a young African American is forced to continue his family's tradition of military service when he is drafted into the United States Army.
